This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with modelling compositionality in natural language semantics. It also involves the use of neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) and "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of tensors, which could place it in the sub-category of "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper also mentions the application of the model to image captioning, which could suggest that it belongs to the sub-category of "cs.CV" (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
